  m_text: "In this game, a button will appear at different positions and sizes.\n\nClick
    it as quickly as possible.\n \nThen rate how difficult the clicking felt in general
    on a 1\u20137 scale:\n\n1 = very easy\n7 = very difficult\n\nKeep the same personal
    standard across rounds. \n\nPress \u201CNext\u201D to continue."
